  <p><seg function="incipit"><milestone n="1r" unit="folio" facs="4"/><lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost"/>mokṣapradāyakaṃ | tava snehān mahādevi vakṣyāmi kavacaṃ śubhaṃ |</seg> <unclear>hrīṃm̐</unclear> bhuvaneśvarīkavacam | śa<unclear>ktri</unclear>ṣir gāyatrī channaḥ <gap reason="lost"/> <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost"/><unclear>śrī</unclear>bhuvaneśvarī devatā catturvargasādhano viniyogaḥ | <unclear>ṛ</unclear>ṣiḥ śaktiḥ śivaḥ pātu gāyatryaṃ <unclear>ānalaṃ</unclear> |  <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost"/>neśvarī | <unclear>ṣa</unclear>ḍaṅgadevatā pātu ṣaṭsv aṅgeṣu mamāniśaṃ |</p>
  <p><milestone n="1v" unit="folio" facs="5"/><lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost"/>vacaṃ | devy uvāca | kathaya sumahādeva jagatī<unclear>ndra</unclear> hitaṃ śubhaṃ | yasya smaraṇamātreṇa palāyante mahāpadāḥ <gap reason="lost"/> <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost"/>sarvarogapraśamanaṃ sarvāpadvinivārakaṃ | sarvaduḥkhāpaharaṇaṃ sarvaśokaprakāśanaṃ | sarvapuṇyapra<gap reason="lost"/> <seg function="explicit"><lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost"/>sarvamaṅgaladāyakaṃ | sarvatīrthaphalakaraṃ sarvayajñaphalapradaṃ | akālamṛtyuśamanaṃ dhanaputrapradāyakaṃ | <gap reason="lost"/></seg></p>
